-- SingTel Chief Executive Officer Chua's Pay Increased 23% to $2.99 Million
-- Andrea Tan
-- 2010-06-29T01:11:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/singtel-chief-executive-officer-chua-s-pay-increased-23-to-2-99-million.html

          
          
             Singapore Telecommunications Ltd.,
Southeast Asia’s biggest phone company, increased Chief
Executive Officer Chua Sock Koong’s pay by 23 percent to S$4.15
million ($2.99 million) last fiscal year, according to the
company’s annual report on its website.  
